  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best online sites to prepare for gate(EE)?",
  "response": "Preparing for the GATE (Graduate Aptitude Test in Engineering) can be a challenging task, and utilizing online resources can greatly help in your preparation. Here are some of the best online sites to prepare for GATE (Electrical Engineering - EE):\n\n1. **NPTEL** (National Programme on Technology Enhanced Learning):\n   - It offers video lectures from IITs and IISc, covering a wide range of subjects relevant to GATE EE.\n   - Website: [NPTEL](https://nptel.ac.in/)\n\n2. **Gradeup** (now BYJU'S Exam Prep):\n   - Provides study materials, mock tests, previous year papers, and live classes.\n   - Website: [BYJU'S Exam Prep](https://byjusexamprep.com/)\n\n3. **Unacademy**:\n   - Offers live classes, doubt-solving sessions, and structured courses by top educators.\n   - Website: [Unacademy](https://unacademy.com/)\n\n4. **Made Easy**:\n   - Known for its focused GATE preparation courses, including study materials, test series, and online classes.\n   - Website: [Made Easy](https://www.madeeasy.in/)\n\n5. **GATE Academy**:\n   - Provides comprehensive study material, video lectures, and test series specifically designed for GATE EE.\n   - Website: [GATE Academy](https://gateacademy.co.in/)\n\n6. **EduRev**:\n   - Offers notes, practice questions, video lectures, and previous year papers for GATE EE.\n   - Website: [EduRev](https://edurev.in/)\n\n7. **Coursera**:\n   - Hosts courses from various universities that can help in understanding fundamental concepts.\n   - Website: [Coursera](https://www.coursera.org/)\n\n8. **Testbook**:\n   - Provides study notes, online tests, previous year question papers, and video lectures.\n   - Website: [Testbook](https://testbook.com/gate-electrical-engineering)\n\n9. **GATEForum**:\n   - Offers online classes, study material, and test series tailored for GATE EE preparation.\n   - Website: [GATEForum](https://gateforum.com/)\n\n10. **Khan Academy**:\n    - Provides free video tutorials on various topics that are essential for GATE EE.\n    - Website: [Khan Academy](https://www.khanacademy.org/)\n\nRemember to check the latest reviews and course updates, as the quality and content of these platforms may evolve over time. Combining resources from multiple sites can give you a comprehensive understanding and better preparation strategy for the GATE exam.",
